data.name: D/D Lamia
data.desc: If this card is in your hand or Graveyard: You can send 1 "D/D" or "Dark Contract" card from your hand or face-up from your field to the Graveyard, except "D/D Lamia"; Special Summon this card, but banish it when it leaves the field. You can only use this effect of "D/D Lamia" once per turn.

card_sets.set_name: Ghosts From the Past: The 2nd Haunting
